subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution ( Fig. 137 ). Present in the southern United States in Texas , as well as in northwestern Mexico , along the coastal slope of the Gulf of Mexico , between the states of Nuevo León , Querétaro , San Luis Potosí , Tamaulipas , and Veracruz , in the following ecoregions (
Dinerstein et al . 2017
): Scrubland of the Central Mexican Plateau, Mesoamerican mangroves of the Gulf and Carribean, Humid forests of Petén-Veracruz, Pine-oak forests of the Sierra Madre Oriental, Mezquital Tamaulipeco, Humid forests of Veracruz , and Coastal grasslands of the Occidental Gulf. Altitudinal distribution from 6 to 1331 m .
